YODL and the distributed macro package can be obtained from
lurl(https://fbb-git.gitlab.io/yodl/). The associated git-repository page is 
located at lurl(https://gitlab.com/fbb-git/yodl).

Yodl can also be retrieved as a binary Debian package: to find it at 
lurl(http://www.debian.org/distrib/packages) by entering tt(yodl) (in any
distribution) in the form-fields you'll find on that page.

